      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The joint meeting Of the Liberty\nPark Improvement club and the\nKickers' Klub last night decided\nto take no action endorsing Civic\nFederation candidates, preferring\nto leave choice open to the in\ndividual voter. The park plan and\nwater extension amendments to the\ncity charter were supported, hut\nthe members were at sea on the\ninitiative and referendum and they\nresolved to study 1t more.\n\n\nThe complaint Of workingman\nthat the First ward bicycle path is\nIn bad shape resulted In the ap.\npointment of committee to take\nthe matter up with the commits\nsion,"
